{"tid":92064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]交警撞車被拋出車外亡　疑未綁安全帶","createTime":"2017-01-23T10:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T17:45:08.000Z","uid":32407,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4b6e5a2d03a8800c083fb67606d614cd690c22","tid":92064,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170123/bkncn-20170123081432337-0123_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170123%2Fbkncn-20170123081432337-0123_05011_001.html&d=U0Pt4ZSIax%2BM6%2FJa6MfzrwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f895b414\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170123/bkncn-20170123081432337-0123_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170123/photo/bkncn-20170123081432337-0123_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170123%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170123081432337-0123_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=0cc9caee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江蘇鹽城東台市前日發生致命車禍，30歲警員丁瑋駕駛警車時遭遇交通事故，與一輛私家車迎頭相撞，警車被撞後四輪朝天，丁瑋經搶救無效死亡。現場照片顯示，死者被拋出車外，事發時或未有綁上安全帶，警方則已定性為「因公殉職」。<br />\n<br />\n東台市警方透過微信公眾號發布通報，指當日上午9時許，東台市交警大隊開發區中隊30歲警員丁瑋駕駛警車，帶領輔警沿城東新區東進大道執勤，途中遭遇交通事故，丁瑋因公殉職。<br />\n<br />\n警方知情人士指，當日一輛私家車與警車相撞，警車被撞到整輛翻轉，損毀嚴重。「路邊的一個水泥墩子也連根拔起，可見撞擊程度有多大。」當地交警表示，正調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1771587243fbe9d7392f656bd9042b11d0c4220","tid":92064,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4294db95085cd5314ff50dde034aa337fa6860a7","tid":92064,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"因公殉職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑死人"},{"pid":"903f844e9b53a35bf3fbb4f9c36eab102ef46e79","tid":92064,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"太少了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf43638dd208fa63952759dff5cf31950432c6e","tid":92064,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}